# Build output — never copy into the Docker image
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/

# IDE / OS noise
.vs/
**/*.user
**/*.suo
_ReSharper*/
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Test results
**/TestResults/
**/coverage/
**/*.trx

# Secrets — should never enter a build context
**/appsettings.Local.json
**/appsettings.Production.json
**/appsettings.Staging.json
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/.secrets.local

# Frontend (not needed by the API build)
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/dist-server/
**/.angular/
